<br>
No one has time any more. Reading a book sometimes, while not taking a long time itself if ya get the time TO sit down and read it, people choose movies because they can do this with others all at once.<br>
<br>
Spending time with friends/family is also something the general public wants to take the time to do. This means popping in a movie, and enjoying it as a group.<br>
<br>
I don't think it will be forgetten where it comes from, but i do know that most people DO forget it comes from books...<br>
<br>
Such as 'Stand By Me' which you mentioned. I wonder how many people know what the book was called by Stephen King. The book wasn't called 'Stand By Me' and that's what most of those that KNOW it came from a book think. Title of the book was, &quot;The Body.&quot;<br>
<br>
The book was a little more dark, but both are good (book or movie) if anyone has the time anymore. <p><!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:green;font-size:x-small;">Arrow Ablaze</span><!--EZCODE FONT END--><!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END--><!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:green;font-size:xx-small;">{54 Pathfinder} </span><!--EZCODE FONT END--><!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END-->==========<!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END--><!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:yellow;font-size:x-small;">Dimora</span><!--EZCODE FONT END--><!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END--><!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:yellow;font-size:xx-small;">{52 Vicar}</span><!--EZCODE FONT END--><!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END-->==========<!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END--><!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:red;font-size:x-small;">Snozynoze</span><!--EZCODE FONT END--><!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END--><!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:red;font-size:xx-small;">{51 Champian}</span><!--EZCODE FONT END--><!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END-->==========<!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END--><!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:orange;font-size:x-small;">Shortauz</span><!--EZCODE FONT END--><!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END--><!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:orange;font-size:xx-small;">{44 Wizard}</span><!--EZCODE FONT END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#102960><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub169.ezboard.com/bmtboards.showUserPublicProfile?gid=shorrtstuff>Shorrtstuff</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>PeeWee Shorrty</span><br>  Posts: 489<br> <font color=#628CBC>(12/21/02 2:24:28 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub169.ezboard.com/fmtboardsfrm5.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=337.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.pennywisdom.com/images/livesch